result.notes: A collection of Non-Native Species sightings from Cornwall and Isles of Scilly Federation for Biological Recorders (CISFBR). The species listed are Bonnemaisonia hamifera, Grateloupia turuturu, Sargassum muticum, Undaria pinnatifida, Spartina anglica, Asterocarpa humilis, Styela clava, Hesperibalanus fallax, Watersipora subatra, Caprella mutica, Diadumene lineata, Crassostrea, Crepidula fornicata and Ficopomatus enigmaticus.
